// Chord Progression Training
// This exercise helps you recognize common chord progressions
// These are the building blocks of most popular music

// === BASIC PROGRESSIONS IN C MAJOR ===

// I-IV-V-I (C-F-G-C) - The most common progression in pop/rock
// "Louie Louie", "Twist and Shout", "Wild Thing"
$: note("<[c,e,g] [f,a,c5] [g,b,d5] [c,e,g]>")
  .scale("C4:major")
  .s("gm_acoustic_guitar_nylon")
  .slow(2)
  .gain(0.8)

